计算文件夹中所有文件的总大小

递归
```python
def get_size(path):
    size = 0
    if os.path.isdir(path):
        for i in os.listdir(path):
            p = os.path.join(path,i)
            if os.path.isdir(p):
                get_size(p)
            else:
                size += os.path.getsize(p)
        return size
    else:
        size += os.path.getsize(path)
        return size
```

循环
```python
def get_size(path):
    l = [path,]
    size = 0
    while l:
        current_path = l.pop()
        for i in os.listdir(current_path):
            p = os.path.join(current_path,i)
            if os.path.isdir(p):
                l.append(p)
            else:
                size += os.path.getsize(p)
    return size
```
